# Complexity
- Time complexity: $$O(n)$$

- Space complexity: $$O(1)$$

# Code
```
class Solution {

    private static final int LINE_WIDTH_PX = 100;

    public int[] numberOfLines(int[] widths, String s) {
        int lines = 0;
        int lastLineWidth = 0;

        for (int i = 0, limit = s.length(), line = LINE_WIDTH_PX; i < limit; i++) {
            int c = s.charAt(i) - 'a';

            int width = widths[c];

            // start new line?
            if (line + width > LINE_WIDTH_PX) {
                line = width;
                lines++;
            } else {
                line += width;
            }

