We count the number of characters in initial String. Then for each word we create a copy of the array with counts and decrement number. If after that the number is < 0 - word cannot be formed. Otherwise - add it's length to result.
Time - O(max(len(chars), L x len(words)) - we do 2 iterations - for for the len of chars to count characters, then L x len(words) - for each word we check every character, L is average length of word. 
Space - O(1) - constant space for number of characters, there will be always constant number of characters.

