# Complexity
- Time complexity: $$O(s * t)$$
<!-- Add your time complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->
where `s` is length of the string in `words` and `t` is length of `target`.

<!-- - Space complexity: -->
<!-- Add your space complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->

