# Intuition
Give Contraints are very small and all string in word vector are of same length, so we need to store the frequency of all characters at ith index in each string in word vector.

And then just recursively check for possible combination by taking each character of target one by one.

# Complexity
- Time complexity:
To store the frequency of characters at ith index = O(word.size()*word[i].length()) 

DP using Memoization = O(word[i].length()*target.length())

- Space complexity:
For frequency matrix = O(word.size()*word[i].length())

For memoization matrix = O(word[i].length()*target.length())

# Code
